    "Training on conflict mediation, proposed by one of the experts, may also be useful.",
    "Such preventative measures are likely to minimize or even avoid failures of the Requirements Elicitation process.",
    "Each of these processes, operates as a set of logically related activities to be completed by all teams, allowing for:",
    "• a better understanding of the situational characteristics of individual development settings; • a clearer comprehension of the cultural orientation of all involved and thus an enhanced cultural awareness and learning; • addressing of potential conflicts arising from differences amongst team members (as defined by Hofstede).",
    "These processes help facilitate change."
